This is a mirror of http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=4385

If you find yourself frequently switching back and forth between files, and looking for a faster way to do it, well, your journey has come to an end. Welcome to the Bufstop! 

Bufstop is a plugin for faster buffer switching, built for efficiency and less keystrokes. It provides no less than 6 ways to display and switch buffers. 

Check out the git repository for a detailed description: https://github.com/mihaifm/bufstop 
